The following issue went on sale today:  Issuer:      Kroger
Manager(s):  Bank of America Merrill Lynch  Mitsubishi Trust International  US Bancorp
Amount:      $450 million
Coupon:      2.2 percent
Maturity:    Jan. 15, 2017
Settlement:  Jan. 19, 2012
Spread:      137.5 basis points more than governments
 